skdetail:

Invocation Name: alphabet animals
des:
Do you know an animal for every letter of the alphabet? With this game Alexa challenges you to guess an animal for all 26 letters of the alphabet. 

I have many fond memories playing this game on car trips with my family so I wanted to bring this fun and educational game to Alexa.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
